---
const doctorImage = '/ale-hands-on.jpeg';

const stats = [
  { value: '15+', label: 'Años de Trayectoria' },
  { value: '2k+', label: 'Cirugías Exitosas' },
  { value: '100%', label: 'Compromiso Ético' },
  { value: '4,9★', label: 'Valoración Pacientes' },
];
---

<section
  id="sobre-mi"
  class="py-24 sm:py-32 relative overflow-hidden"
  style="background-color: #8E5E61;"
>
  <!-- Decorative blobs -->
  <div class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-[36rem] h-[36rem] bg-black/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-transparent via-white/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">

      <!-- Texto (orden 2 en mobile) -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 animate-on-scroll from-left">
        <span class="section-label mb-6 block w-fit" style="background-color: rgba(226,151,156,0.2); color: #FADCD2; border-color: rgba(250,220,210,0.3);">
          Sobre la Doctora
        </span>

        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-display italic font-bold mb-8 leading-tight text-beige">
          Ciencia, Arte y Compromiso Médico
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-base sm:text-lg font-light italic leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(249,245,240,0.75);">
          <p>
            Con más de 15 años de experiencia en el ámbito de la cirugía plástica, estética y reparadora, mi misión es brindar un espacio de seguridad y confianza para mis pacientes en Mendoza.
          </p>
          <p>
            Soy miembro titular de las principales sociedades científicas del país, lo que avala mi compromiso con la actualización constante y la ética profesional en cada procedimiento.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats grid -->
        <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
          {stats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="border-t pt-5 animate-on-scroll" style="border-color: rgba(249,245,240,0.2);">
              <span class="block font-black text-primary" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 1;">
                {stat.value}
              </span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-bold" style="color: rgba(249,245,240,0.45);">
                {stat.label}
              </span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Sociedades médicas placeholder -->
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t flex flex-wrap gap-6 items-center" style="border-color: rgba(249,245,240,0.15);">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-bold" style="color: rgba(249,245,240,0.35);">Miembro de:</div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="background-color: rgba(249,245,240,0.1); color: rgba(249,245,240,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(249,245,240,0.15);">
              SACPER
            </div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="background-color: rgba(249,245,240,0.1); color: rgba(249,245,240,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(249,245,240,0.15);">
              ISAPS
            </div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="background-color: rgba(249,245,240,0.1); color: rgba(249,245,240,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(249,245,240,0.15);">
              AAC Mendoza
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen (orden 1 en mobile) -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-on-scroll from-right">
        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-sm sm:max-w-md lg:max-w-none">
          <!-- Decorative rotated background -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/25 rounded-[3.5rem] rotate-6 scale-105 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 rounded-[3.5rem] -rotate-3 scale-102 pointer-events-none"></div>

          <!-- Doctor image -->
          <img
            src={doctorImage}
            alt="Retrato profesional de la Dra. Alejandra D'Ovidio con bata médica"
            class="relative rounded-[3.5rem] w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover shadow-2xl"
            style="border: 8px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />

          <!-- Floating credential card -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-4 sm:-bottom-8 sm:-right-8 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-md" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400;">verified</span>
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-beige">Certificada</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-bold" style="color: rgba(249,245,240,0.5);">MN 10.544 · Mendoza</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
